{"tid":11611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（av)日本女護士旅行印度 慘被強姦","createTime":"2016-11-29T10:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T12:47:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6bf0953a1eae738b4fd33be574ea8d30e0692ab0","tid":11611,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:46:24.000Z","msg":"印度再發生遊客被強姦事件。 <br />\n<br />\n一名日本女遊客上周六在南部喀拉拉邦度假勝地庫瓦蘭（Kovalam）遭一名當地人強姦，酒店職員翌日早上發現受害人流血，將她送院，警方周日拘捕一名25歲涉案男子。 <br />\n該名日本女遊客是一名護士，兩周前到訪印度，上周六案發前數小時才抵達庫瓦蘭。警方稱，被捕男子的家人在當地旅遊景點開設手工藝品店。暫未知他與受害人如何認識。 <br />\n印度涉及遊客的風化案頻生，去年初一名22歲日本女遊客遭6名男子禁錮輪姦，一個月後亦有一名日本女遊客遭當地導遊強姦。"},{"pid":"5da1f4e886f37b0c59f84bf1a38804e5659a0280","tid":11611,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:47:00.000Z","msg":"下海咪得囉..."},{"pid":"d537ea927a95286393716a4c951fc1e371a8b985","tid":11611,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:47:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f483614d9cb57b18075465a93577a502821ab1","tid":11611,"uid":10733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:49:38.000Z","msg":"On9國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c28bf0b4a24cb6daa5df4d783e78cf9dea66c5","tid":11611,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:50:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf96b9f10b449ae337f58cdabc09f8dd6d23757d","tid":11611,"uid":20524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:52:39.000Z","msg":"av情節"},{"pid":"be2f26e101872007e019522dfe7b38bb7766d462","tid":11611,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:58:08.000Z","msg":"點解要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm